%% API Key Interaction Sequence
%% Authenticated CRUD operation flow

sequenceDiagram
    actor Client
    participant Gateway
    participant Auth
    participant Service
    participant DB

    Client->>Gateway: POST /resource (+ API key)
    Gateway->>Auth: Validate API key
    Auth-->>Gateway: Authorized
    Gateway->>Service: Create resource
    Service->>DB: INSERT
    DB-->>Service: Created
    Service-->>Gateway: 201 Created
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON response
